name: .SUB Data Use Agreement Tags v0.2. [timelimit, sharing, reidentify, publication, use, acceptance, approval].

children.name: DUA 1. Set timelimit tag.
. timelimit tag is one of {none, 1yr, 2yr, 5yr}.
. A qualified user may be required to delete all copies of the data based on a time limit.
DUA 1.1. May a qualified person use the data indefinitely?
Yes. DUA 1.1.1. GOTO DUA 2. DUAtags= [timelimit=none,___,___,___,___,___,___,___].
No. DUA 1.2. May a qualified person use the data for 1 year?
Yes. DUA 1.2.1. GOTO DUA 2. DUAtags= [timelimit=1yr,___,___,___,___,___,___,___].
No. DUA 1.3. May a qualified person use the data for 2 years?
Yes. DUA 1.3.1. GOTO DUA 2. DUAtags= [timelimit=2yr,___,___,___,___,___,___,___].
No. DUA 1.4. May a qualified person use the data for 5 years?
Yes. DUA 1.4.1. GOTO DUA 2. DUAtags= [timelimit=5yr,___,___,___,___,___,___,___].
GOTO DUA 1
DUA 2. Set sharing tag.
. sharing tag is one of {anyone, not online, organization, group, no one}
DUA 2.1. May a qualified person share the data with others freely?
Yes. DUA 2.1.1. GOTO DUA 3. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=anyone,___,___,___,___,___,___].
No. DUA 2.2. May a qualified person share the data with others provided the data is not made publicly available online?
Yes. DUA 2.2.1. GOTO DUA 3. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=not online,___,___,___,___,___,___].
No. DUA 2.3. May a qualified person share the data with others in his organization?
Yes. DUA 2.3.1. GOTO DUA 3. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=organization,___,___,___,___,___,___].
No. DUA 2.3. May a qualified person share the data with others in his immediate work group?
Yes. DUA 2.4.1. GOTO DUA 3. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=group,___,___,___,___,___,___].
No. DUA 2.4. Is a qualified recipient prohibited from sharing the data with anyone?
Yes. DUA 2.5.1. GOTO DUA 3. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=no one,___,___,___,___,___,___].
GOTO DUA 2
DUA 3. Set reidentify tag.
. reidentify tag is one of {no matching, no entities, no people, no prohibition, reidentify, contact}
DUA 3.1. Is a qualified person prohibited from matching data to other data?
Yes. DUA 3.1.1. GOTO DUA 4. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify=no matching,___,___,___,___,___].
No. DUA 3.2. Is a qualified recipient prohibited from identifying and contacting people or organizations in the data?
Yes. DUA 3.2.1. GOTO DUA 4. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify=no entities,___,___,___,___,___].
No. DUA 3.3. Is a qualified recipient prohibited from identifying and contacting people whose information is in the data?
Yes. DUA 3.3.1. GOTO DUA 4. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify=no people,___,___,___,___,___].
No. DUA 3.4. Is a qualified person allowed to re-identify and contact people whose information is in the data?
Yes. DUA 3.4.1. GOTO DUA 4. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,no prohibition,___,___,___,___,___].
No. DUA 3.5. Is a qualified person allowed to re-identify but not contact people whose information is in the data?
Yes. DUA 3.5.1. GOTO DUA 4. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify,___,___,___,___,___].
No. DUA 3.6. Is a qualified person allowed to contact people whose information is in the data?
Yes. DUA 3.6.1. GOTO DUA 4. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,contact,___,___,___,___,___].
GOTO DUA 3
DUA 4. Set publication tag.
. publication tag is one of {no restriction, notify, pre-approve, prohibited}
DUA 4.1. May a qualified user freely publish papers using the data?
Yes. DUA 4.1.1. GOTO DUA 5. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify=no matching,publication=no restriction,___,___,___,___].
No. DUA 4.2. Must a qualified recipient notify you of any publications using the data?
Yes. DUA 4.2.1. GOTO DUA 5. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify=no entities,publication=notify,___,___,___,___].
No. DUA 4.3. Must a qualified recipient get your pre-approval before publishing a paper that uses the data?
Yes. DUA 4.3.1. GOTO DUA 5. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify=no people,publication=pre-approve,___,___,___,___].
No. DUA 4.4. Are there to be no publications using your data?
Yes. DUA 4.4.1. GOTO DUA 5. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,no prohibition,publication=prohibited,___,___,___,___].
GOTO DUA 4
DUA 5. Set use tag.
. use tag is one of {no restriction, research, IRB, no product}
DUA 5.1. May a qualified user freely use the data for any purpose?
Yes. DUA 5.1.1. GOTO DUA 5. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify=no matching,publication=SET,use=no restriction,___,___,___].
No. DUA 5.2. Must a qualified recipient use the data for research only?
Yes. DUA 5.2.1. GOTO DUA 5. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify=no entities,publication=SET,use=research,___,___,___].
No. DUA 5.3. Must a qualified recipient use the data for IRB approved research only?
Yes. DUA 5.3.1. GOTO DUA 5. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify=no people,publication=SET,use=IRB,___,___,___].
No. DUA 5.4. Is a qualified user prohibited from incorporating the data into products or other data?
Yes. DUA 5.4.1. GOTO DUA 5. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,no prohibition,publication=SET,use=no product,___,___,___].
GOTO DUA 6
DUA 6. Set acceptance tag.
. acceptance tag is one of {click, sign, sign with ID}
DUA 6.1. May a qualified user agree to these terms of data use by clicking on an acknowledgement?
Yes. DUA 6.1.1. GOTO DUA 6. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify=no matching,publication=SET,use=SET,acceptance=click,___,___].
No. DUA 6.2. Must a qualified user agree to these terms by submitting a digitally signed version?
Yes. DUA 6.2.1. GOTO DUA 6. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify=no entities,publication=SET,use=SET,acceptance=sign,___,___].
No. DUA 6.3. Must a qualified user agree to these terms by submitting a copy physically signed with a copy of a government issued ID?
Yes. DUA 6.3.1. GOTO DUA 6. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify=no people,publication=SET,use=IRB,acceptance=sign with ID,___,___].
GOTO DUA 7
DUA 7. Set approval tag.
. approval tag is one of {none, email, signed}
DUA 7.1. May a qualified user use the data with no further approval from you?
Yes. DUA 7.1.1. GOTO DUA 6. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify=no matching,publication=SET,use=SET,acceptance=SET,approval=none].
No. DUA 7.2. Do you want to approve each application for use by email?
Yes. DUA 7.2.1. GOTO DUA 6. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify=no entities,publication=SET,use=SET,acceptance=SET,approval=email].
No. DUA 7.3. Do you want to approve each application by submitting your digitally signed approval?
Yes. DUA 7.3.1. GOTO DUA 6. DUAtags= [timelimit=SET,sharing=SET,reidentify=no people,publication=SET,use=IRB,acceptance=SET,approval=signed].
GOTO DUA 8
DUA 8. END.
